1�I am Myffore. I watch this door, for unspeakable terrors lurk on the far side.
1�I can open the door for you, but quickly I must close it. Once inside, you must find some other way out.
1�Do you want me to open the door?Yes. I am not afraid.No, thank you.
1�Wait.
1�I changed my mind. Please, let me throw it in myself.
1�Ten... No, a hundred years from now, if the bracelet is ever found, what will cross their minds? Could it be true that the memories of past owners reside within such things?
1�And when I think how we may yet find such a thing, recovering memories buried under the flow of time, it seems sad.
1�Thank you for helping me. Everything seems much clearer now. Here, take this.
1�Beware, as the pass before you is extremely dangerous. Even the most traveled adventurers have stepped through that door, never to return.
1�In the depths of Ranguemont Pass there is a small pond.I remember...it was almost dawn after a night of the full moon.It was there that I saw the shadow.
1�In the depths of Ranguemont Pass there is a small pond.Though much time has passed, I remember...it was almost dawn after a night of the full moon.It was there that I saw the shadow.
1�At first, I thought it was just one of those slime creatures.But it was far too big for that, and seemed to be wrapped in robes...
1�Sensing that this was no monster, I began to edge closer...The shadow turned towards me.
..�That dreadful countenance!It was like a creature born from nightmares...I drew my sword, only to have it wrenched from my grasp by some unknown power.
1�But I have trained as a knight.
1�I quickly recovered and drew my lesser blade, slicing into the thing's robes.What spilled from its body was not the blood I expected, but light!
1�Thinking about it now, I wonder if that #???? wasn't just something the creature had been carrying...
1�Travel to the pond and see what you can find. I'm counting on you.
1�I want you to take that to the Mithra.She said she was heading for Jugner Forest.
1�There is a merchant staying by the lake in Jugner Forest who is said to have seen the bearer of darkness.If you find the merchant, you will likely find the Sibyl Guard.
1�Did you give the envelope to the Sibyl Guard?
